Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I really have it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ten years already...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.32,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, dear me!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family heirloom is a clay figure. {家宝は、埴輪です}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ski too? Wonderful!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'm good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmerizing indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean my dress?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.96,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you can't be serious! \NI would know!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.32,0:02:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you for coming to the Ijuuin Christmas party that we take great pride in.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.67,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forget the everyday routine \Nand enjoy yourselves to the fullest today.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.86,0:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please check your coat \Nat cloakroom over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.83,0:02:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep this tag until you leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.59,0:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.84,0:03:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've opened hotel in Hawaii recently.\NYou should come visit next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's so gorgeous!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, quite extravagant.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! So that's how it was?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Male guests are required to wear a neck tie.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.44,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure no more unwanted rabble \Nslips into the party.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.94,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything improper happens to our female guests, it’ll disgrace the Ijuuin family name.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I’ve already made \Nall the necessary arrangements.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.63,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The special response unit \Nis deployed outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Sotoi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.06,0:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was my own inattention...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.94,0:04:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I know her? \NWho is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do for the New Year's holidays?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I studied the whole time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The closest thing I did to celebrating \Nwas going to the shrine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The school starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.19,0:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At your school too?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to see him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.82,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, ever since the school had already permitted it,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.41,0:07:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of starting an after-school activity. {/event}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An activity?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! {}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For god's sake, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.40,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we're not in the same grade, \NI'll be doing same things senpai does.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already sharing the hardships!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.71,0:08:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have the time for that, \Nwhy not provide emotional support instead?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.41,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Another third-year girl from senpai's class \Nis treating him to her bento.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.29,0:08:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my senpai, all right! \NHe's hot as fire! {popular}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Himoo-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.90,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now... \NI'm Saotome Yoshio of Class A.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the informant?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's one way to put it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not anything in particular...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.21,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Come to think of it, I heard you got a job offer from one of the leading companies.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left for you \Nis to just wait until the graduation.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.92,0:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've nothing to do, \Nhow about a date?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have things to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.74,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't graduate and let it drag behind me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.11,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I’d have a third-year student \Nstill going back and forth about her future…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you decided?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a job that you'd like to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.86,0:09:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There is, like a news anchor, \Nor an entertainment reporter.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.09,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A stylist is good too, or a designer...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.95,0:09:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. The winter holidays ended so soon!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.32,0:10:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring holidays will come \Nin just two months, stay strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.47,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The piece we just listened to \Nis Chopin's Piano Concerto No.2 in F minor.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.00,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This piece was written by Chopin \Nin collaboration with Konstancja Kładkowska,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.64,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a vocal student at the Warsaw Conservatory.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.29,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She was Chopin's first love.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.88,0:11:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite his enormous talent, \NChopin couldn't bring himself to confess to her.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.13,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In later years, it was said that she didn't even remember Chopin's name.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.19,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm a bit late, \Nbut do you mind me joining the session?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.96,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Well, I'm sorry, \Nbut we're done for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't borrow the music room for too long.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.49,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, that's a pity.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.37,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consolation, why don't I use \Nthe Ijuuin limousine to drive you all home?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.17,0:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't done anything \Nto deserve that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.30,0:12:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I must go \Nto the cram school right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.82,0:12:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I promised mom \Nto go shopping after school.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.64,0:12:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori-kun, perhaps you also \Nhave some errands to run after school?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? No, I don't...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.36,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.66,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not fair! Rei-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.10,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori-kun, why did you decide \Nto start that kind of after-school activity? {(program of) entertainments; special events; exhibitions; amusements; attractions}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our high school life \Nis nearing its completion.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.50,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not the most straightforward explanation,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.24,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanted to do something \Nthat would leave a memory.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.32,0:13:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? Who knows, maybe that person \Nwill also come to listen to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.02,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all I could do.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.79,0:13:31.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,The company suits have just called.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,If you don’t give them an answer today,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,you might as well pretend \Nthe offer never existed.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyclamen...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.04,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flower language, you mean shyness.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like me...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! To think I'd get to eat your bento! {虹弁が食えるなんて - Nijino Saki (虹野沙希) is the girl on the right, who promised to make bentos in ep1}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you need to keep your spirits high.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is that obvious my spirits are low?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.28,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My! That's really cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This stuff totally doesn't suit me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.46,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All I do is swimming, \Nso my body shape is like that of a boy. {水泳ばかりしてたから、体型も逆さんだし}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say something?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.62,0:15:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he cares for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.73,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.81,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A little, you know, insecure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're growing your hair long...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.26,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, auntie? Hi! It's me, Ayako.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. No matter what?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll never come, after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, keep it quiet back there!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.12,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to stay out \Nin this cold all day long, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shiori, did you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.93,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.33,0:17:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy and Kagami from Class H \Nwent on a date.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.69,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they've got time to spare, even though the exams are right around the corner!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.44,0:17:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... You answered so fast, \Nit caught me by surprise!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to say... \NSomething really good happened today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just watching...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.41,0:18:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watching him is good enough..."
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't tell him...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about my feelings, \Nhe might never notice.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.72,0:18:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.31,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't find the courage for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.24,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshio-kun, can we talk?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.34,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Yoshio! What did Fujisaki \Nsay to you just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked for a phone number... {not his}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Kagami.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is calling?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It broke!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You broke it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.08,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Oh god... Will you two stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.08,0:19:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Just stop for a minute! \NYou'll get hurt if you step on the pieces!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you hear? You need to stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.87,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.10,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.91,0:20:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, great job, you two! I already missed out \Non a date because of you, and now this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it? \NWhat did you call me here for?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to learn breaststroke next?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.83,0:20:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.05,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A present for you. \NPlease accept it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so sudden... Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.30,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work, swimming. {from now on}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.30,0:20:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we're going to listen \Nto Beethoven's Piano Sonata No. 14.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Moonlight" in C sharp minor.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.52,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This piece was dedicated to Countess Giulietta Guicciardi, who was Beethoven's piano teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The title of this piece, Moonlight,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.63,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was not chosen in accordance with the composer's own vision,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.53,0:21:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather coined by the German critic...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.93,0:21:04.51,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Mira-kun, that classmate of mine...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What was his name...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't know him well, \Nbut I've heard you two are going out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please don't misunderstand...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was merely a charity for an unpopular boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.23,0:21:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted him to have \Nsome nice memories of his high school days.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.43,0:21:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, let's get started.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Going abroad? Our Ayako?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.60,0:21:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's something she's been considering for a long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.00,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She has an aunt living abroad, \Nso she's going to study in earnest now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's brave...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.08,0:21:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get injured and can no longer swim,\N I will have nothing left of my life.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.28,0:22:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the same for everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.22,0:22:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That flower is Lavender, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.62,0:22:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's the birth flower \Nfor my birthday, December 3rd. {うん、あたしの誕生日、十二月三日の誕生花だ}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.92,0:22:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In flower language, it's "hope."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.13,0:22:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she always looks so untroubled...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.14,0:24:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't stop doing what I love?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.75,0:24:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:48.72,0:24:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've decided?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.20,0:24:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I have it written \Nall over my face, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.01,0:25:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck. I'll keep cheering for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.29,0:25:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said, \Nall I can do is make bento for you...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.62,0:25:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.04,0:25:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, there must be someone else \Nthat you need to cook them for.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.17,0:25:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to make them \Nfor someone who's always doing her best.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.73,0:25:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonjour, bonsoir.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:28.28,0:25:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oui, c'est ca. Je voudrais...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:32.89,0:25:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,France, huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:37.56,0:25:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats! This time for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:40.66,0:25:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai likes... me!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.90,0:25:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are. It's me!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:46.40,0:25:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this? I bought a cell phone.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:48.88,0:25:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No one calls from public phones these days.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:59.08,0:26:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.42,0:26:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I can conquer the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.63,0:26:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:07.76,0:26:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.18,0:26:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends, although it was only for a short time,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:12.53,0:26:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you all for joining us \Nfor all the listening sessions.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.20,0:26:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I planned this kind of after-school activity with graduation just around the corner
Dialogue: 10,0:26:22.21,0:26:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because I wanted to leave something behind \Nfrom my three years at this school.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.71,0:26:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to spend as much time as possible with people I did not yet knew personally,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.11,0:26:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,even though we were in the same school.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.20,0:26:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:40.35,0:26:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.81,0:26:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you ever so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:45.42,0:26:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our graduation is just a week away.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:47.73,0:26:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, the following piece \Nwill become our final listening session.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:52.20,0:26:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mozart Piano Concerto No. 27.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:56.25,0:27:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This song is rumored to have been written for Magdalena Hofdemel,
Dialogue: 10,0:27:00.30,0:27:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,who is believed to have been \NMozart's last mistress.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:05.02,0:27:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, please enjoy.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:28.42,0:27:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one week left, huh? \NThese three years really flew by.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:33.34,0:27:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still one last important event \Nbefore we wrap up our high school days.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:37.80,0:27:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Event?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:40.43,0:27:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:27:41.70,0:27:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what is she doing there.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.56,0:27:56.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's a bit embarrassing for me to talk about, \Nbut I just couldn't get your image out of my head.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:59.75,0:28:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know, Shiori-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:01.91,0:28:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a myth going around \Nour Kirameki High.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:07.31,0:28:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a myth that if a girl confesses her love to a boy on graduation day under that tree,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:13.18,0:28:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the two will be able to live happily ever after...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:17.31,0:28:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you tell others, it will lose its effect.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.60,0:28:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The myth of Kirameki High?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:23.20,0:28:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And that tree \Nis the one from the myth.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:31.57,0:28:34.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,Graduation is in three days
Dialogue: 10,0:28:44.77,0:28:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... Actually, I've always... {rehearsing the confession}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:52.92,0:28:55.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't have the courage...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:36.47,0:29:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:39.14,0:29:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:41.89,0:29:43.95,Top,,0,0,0,,The low pressure front keeps moving eastward,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.95,0:29:47.36,Top,,0,0,0,,and the high pressure front \Ncoming from the conflict is gaining strength.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:47.36,0:29:52.11,Top,,0,0,0,,The clouds will move eastward from Kanto, \Nso it's going to be sunny starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.11,0:29:56.02,Top,,0,0,0,,However, it'll still be chilly tonight\Nand may turn to snow in some places.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:58.24,0:30:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, what are you grinning at in the mirror? {I would write her name but I don't fucking remember what any of them are called}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:01.84,0:30:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kids should already be in bed by now!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:04.43,0:30:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.58,0:30:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,G'night.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:07.81,0:30:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, sis.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:09.24,0:30:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:17.30,0:30:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The back...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.34,0:30:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of a boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:26.31,0:30:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... \NWhat do I do after I chop these up?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:37.31,0:31:39.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Robo.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.48,0:32:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:55.53,0:32:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:00.42,0:33:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss No-name Caller?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:03.06,0:33:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:04.66,0:33:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:07.18,0:33:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:11.17,0:33:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:14.74,0:33:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My love...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.00,0:33:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,died. {/is over}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:25.92,0:33:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand why...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:28.13,0:33:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That person always had an eye \Nfor another girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:32.97,0:33:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it all along.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:38.08,0:33:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first met her at school, \NI thought she was nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:41.60,0:33:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But for him, it was love at first sight.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:44.80,0:33:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know how to approach him, \Nhow to speak up.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:49.13,0:33:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to just take the plunge...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:52.86,0:33:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,His shocked expression \Nis still vivid in my memory.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:57.94,0:34:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I would also often walk past him \Nso that he could remember my face. {顔を覚えてもらうために、先回りしたこともあったわ - very unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:04.03,0:34:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was good enough \Neven if I don't tell him anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:07.25,0:34:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought just watching him \Nwas good enough...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:13.67,0:34:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I was terribly wrong...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:18.11,0:34:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand just watching him \Nand then part forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.54,0:34:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I mustered all of my courage today \Nand called him on the phone.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.36,0:34:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking down the avenue with that person...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:33.46,0:34:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I pictured it in my heart the whole time!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:38.54,0:34:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was to become a wonderful memory. {also unsure: その人と一緒に並木道を歩いたずっとずっと、心の中で思い描いてたの素敵な思い出になった}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:43.83,0:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was meant...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:46.78,0:34:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was meant to be a wonderful day!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:06.40,0:35:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:12.65,0:35:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have courage,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:15.11,0:35:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki Shiori-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:17.31,0:35:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:18.23,0:35:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feelings will surely reach him....
Dialogue: 10,0:35:21.62,0:35:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They will reach the person you love!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:26.36,0:35:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been bothering you for so long...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:28.50,0:35:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This will become the final call \Nof the no-name caller.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.15,0:35:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait... Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.59,0:35:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:39.26,0:35:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it with all the courage you can muster...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:29.05,0:36:30.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,My feelings...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:31.42,0:36:33.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,The feelings that he never noticed
Dialogue: 10,0:36:34.89,0:36:37.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,are still growing ever-stronger.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:37.86,0:36:39.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,Our time together,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:40.03,0:36:42.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,the three years we spent here...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:43.56,0:36:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! Do you remember this?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:46.30,0:36:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mark from when we compared \Nour heights about ten years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:50.73,0:36:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great sense of mystery...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:53.28,0:36:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep watching \Nthe stars like this forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:59.29,0:37:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a cake. \NWould you come to my place?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:04.93,0:37:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we look \Nlike a couple right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.37,0:37:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I just felt like \Nspooking you a bit there.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:25.27,0:37:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty! It's a White Christmas!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:31.65,0:37:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to know, \NI just prayed for some courage.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:38.59,0:37:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that giving you this at school \Nwould be too embarrassing.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:42.29,0:37:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I put my very special feelings \Ninto this chocolate.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:49.37,0:37:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sought this CD for a long time.\NI'll make sure to treasure it!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:56.90,0:38:02.89,Top,,0,0,0,,And today, the time has come for you \Nto graduate from this temple of knowledge.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:04.41,0:38:07.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all the wonderful memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:10.24,0:38:13.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm lucky to have a childhood friend like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:16.49,0:38:17.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's not true...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:26.79,0:38:27.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:29.00,0:38:31.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,Not just a childhood friend...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:31.94,0:38:34.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't want it to become just a memory...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:34.73,0:38:36.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:36.23,0:38:37.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,Because!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:37.40,0:38:38.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:38.73,0:38:40.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,I...!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.40,0:39:42.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him with all the courage I have...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:43.12,0:39:45.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,how I'm feeling right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:46.80,0:39:49.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him under the old tree from the myth!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:50.26,0:39:53.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,About my love for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:54.78,0:39:58.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him, the person I love.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:20.09,0:40:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you \Ncome all the way here.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:27.71,0:40:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need \Nto tell you today, no matter what.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:36.21,0:40:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've never dated a boy up until now...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:44.05,0:40:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that's not to say I'm disinterested.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:48.66,0:40:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I would really like to date a boy, if I could.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:54.06,0:40:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've even received \Na few love letters in the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:00.23,0:41:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:02.24,0:41:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, \NI didn't feel like going out with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:07.83,0:41:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:10.99,0:41:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were by my side.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:16.15,0:41:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now, I've always thought of you\Nas nothing but a childhood friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:24.02,0:41:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:25.90,0:41:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just too scared \Nto reveal my true feelings to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:32.28,0:41:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's what I thought...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:36.14,0:41:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:38.20,0:41:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,now that we have to graduate...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:41.07,0:41:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we must go our separate ways \Nand may never meet again,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:46.15,0:41:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally realized what I feel.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:52.05,0:41:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel embarrassed and want to run away,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:58.04,0:41:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but I...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:00.31,0:42:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to stay just childhood friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:05.15,0:42:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be the only girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:08.72,0:42:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that you look at.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:13.24,0:42:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll muster my courage
Dialogue: 10,0:42:16.27,0:42:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:22.48,0:42:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:25.28,0:42:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I only love you
Dialogue: 10,0:42:28.80,0:42:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with all the love in the world. {feeling creative, lit: I love you more than anyone else in this world}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:43.67,0:42:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:47.02,0:42:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be really happy now, \Nbut I can't stop crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:51.77,0:42:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever, ever let me go.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:21.75,0:43:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's topic: one last word.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:25.59,0:43:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Performing for you: Tatebayashi Miharu, \Nvoiced by Shiho Kikuchi (菊池 志穂).
Dialogue: 10,0:43:28.67,0:43:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I believe in love at [UwU]
Dialogue: 10,0:43:31.19,0:43:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I believe in love at first sight!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:35.14,0:43:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikihara Megumi, \Nby Mikiko Kurihara (栗原 みきこ).
Dialogue: 10,0:43:37.49,0:43:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna do it for another 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:40.39,0:43:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:44.15,0:43:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Asahina Yuuko, Yoko Teppouzuka (鉄炮塚 葉子).
Dialogue: 10,0:43:46.36,0:43:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:48.78,0:43:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Asahina-san will do her best from now on,\NI'll also give it my best.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:52.30,0:43:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you all stay well.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:58.58,0:44:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisaragi Mio, Akiko Sekine (関根 明子).
Dialogue: 10,0:44:01.01,0:44:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:04.52,0:44:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very wonderful memorial.\N- Akiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:08.33,0:44:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Himoo Yuina, Tomoko Naka (中 友子).
Dialogue: 10,0:44:10.17,0:44:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, it was fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:12.05,0:44:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree? \NIt was so much fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:14.46,0:44:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little sad that I'm graduating.\NHere's one last word from me:
Dialogue: 10,0:44:18.95,0:44:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo, go!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:22.56,0:44:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:24.40,0:44:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome Yumi, Kurin Yoshiki (よしき くりん).
Dialogue: 10,0:44:26.61,0:44:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for sticking with us all this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:29.71,0:44:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that every ending \Nis also a new beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:33.34,0:44:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun, I agree. \NA lot has happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:37.09,0:44:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:38.84,0:44:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So my last word is,
Dialogue: 10,0:44:40.51,0:44:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Next is big brother!"
Dialogue: 10,0:44:43.16,0:44:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, thanks...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:45.18,0:44:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot? Kurin! (Yoshiki)
Dialogue: 10,0:44:46.41,0:44:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did forget.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:47.96,0:44:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Saotome Yoshio, Yuuji Ueda (うえだ ゆうじ).
Dialogue: 10,0:44:50.83,0:44:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,May you have a nightmare tonight...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:55.82,0:44:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:58.35,0:45:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Katagiri Ayako, Masayo Kawaguchi (川口 雅代).
Dialogue: 10,0:45:00.44,0:45:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for my last word, I just want to say I love you and I'm gonna miss you.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:04.66,0:45:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck and goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:06.16,0:45:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} are my treasure forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:08.87,0:45:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:10.08,0:45:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With love from New York, thank you for your hard work, everyone. Masayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:23.08,0:45:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nijino Saki, Sachiko Sugawara (菅原 祥子).
Dialogue: 10,0:45:26.33,0:45:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugawara.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:28.16,0:45:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was very fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:30.48,0:45:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a really long time, \Nenough for my hair to grow long again.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:33.73,0:45:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for sticking around!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:37.80,0:45:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see everyone like this again.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:40.78,0:45:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope to see you in a year or two.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:42.87,0:45:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Sugawara Sachiko!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:47.68,0:45:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin Rei, Narumi Tsunoda (津野田 なるみ).
Dialogue: 10,0:45:49.96,0:45:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do, peasants!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:53.59,0:45:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for sticking around. Narumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:00.20,0:46:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Koshiki Yukari, Ayako Kurosaki (黒崎 彩子).
Dialogue: 10,0:46:06.08,0:46:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, really, really! \NThank you for a long, long, long time with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:13.54,0:46:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown up to be a lot more responsible.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:15.56,0:46:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:16.84,0:46:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that? \NAyako.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:19.65,0:46:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyokawa Nozomi, Ayako Sasaki (笹木 綾子).
Dialogue: 10,0:46:22.23,0:46:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,During this year, my skirt just kept getting shorter and shorter.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:27.49,0:46:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It only got a little longer at the end, \Nwhen I had an operation, LOL. {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:31.25,0:46:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet again somewhere. Ayako.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:35.40,0:46:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami Mira, Rei Igarashi (五十嵐 麗).
Dialogue: 10,0:46:42.78,0:46:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Since this is the last time, \NI thought I'd say my thanks to everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:47.50,0:46:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:49.87,0:46:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:52.19,0:46:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone, it was really fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:55.40,0:46:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:56.61,0:46:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Kagami-san! {idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:58.43,0:46:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This was Rei.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:09.85,0:47:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:11.20,0:47:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki Shiori, Mami Kingetsu (金月 真美).
Dialogue: 10,0:47:13.90,0:47:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really grateful to all the different people I've got to meet.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:19.59,0:47:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a very enjoyable few years.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:23.28,0:47:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And I ended up saying it too...
Dialogue: 10,0:47:28.91,0:47:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but really, I want to say this on behalf of all the cast and staff,
Dialogue: 10,0:47:37.02,0:47:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much for your support!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:39.73,0:47:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remember us again somewhere, sometime. Mami.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:45.11,0:47:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange glasses!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:47.56,0:47:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to mention the glasses!
