Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.97,0:05:28.60,Song,,0,0,0,,Since when have you become afraid of getting hurt? {傷つくこと　いつからか怖くなって\N踏み出す勇気　なくしたの？\N信じること　少しだけつらくなって\Nめくもりさえも　見失いそうなの？\N\Nでも　そんな気持ち\N目をそらさずに見つめていけたら\N君は素敵\N今日よりも　昨日よりも\N\N思いきり傷ついて　ほんとの優しさ知ればいい\Nもっと遠く　飛び立てる\N失って悩んでも　信じた心　誇ればいい\Nまっすぐ胸を張り　歩きだせる\N\N夢見たこと　追いつづけるときには\N冷たく強い　風も吹く\N思いのまま　歩きつづけることは\N孤独でひとり　泣きたくなるけど}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.60,0:05:34.81,Song,,0,0,0,,Where did the courage to take a step forward go?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.65,0:05:44.41,Song,,0,0,0,,Believing has become a little harder than before
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.41,0:05:52.41,Song,,0,0,0,,Now even warmth is slipping away—\Nare you just going to let it go?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.42,Song,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.92,0:06:01.88,Song,,0,0,0,,If I embrace those feelings\Nand gaze at you without looking away,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.88,0:06:10.10,Song,,0,0,0,,you are fabulous—\Nmore than today, more than yesterday
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.10,0:06:19.61,Song,,0,0,0,,Only when you get hurt really deeply, \Nyou'll learn what the true kindness is
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.61,0:06:25.36,Song,,0,0,0,,You'll learn to fly much farther
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.36,0:06:29.22,Song,,0,0,0,,You can be proud of what you believed in,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.22,0:06:34.88,Song,,0,0,0,,even if you've lost it and can't get over it
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.88,0:06:43.99,Song,,0,0,0,,Throw your chest confidently out \Nand start walking
Dialogue: 5,0:24:30.49,0:24:38.26,Song,,0,0,0,,When you keep chasing what you once dreamed, {"Beginning" again}{夢見たこと　追いつづけるときには\N冷たく強い　風も吹く\N思いのまま　歩きつづけることは\N孤独でひとり　泣きたくなるけど\N\Nでも　信じていて\N君が決めたことだから　迷わず\N世界がほら　ひらくたび　素敵になる\N\N熱いほど焦がれてる夢なら　かたちにすればいい\Nもっと強く　しなやかに\N立ち止まり迷ったら　もう一度　素直になればいい\N輝く明日が　君を待ってる\N\N幸せになれるから　心をかるく解き放して\Nもっと高く　飛び立てる\N二度とない一瞬を　君らしく抱きしめればいい\N未来へとつづいてく\N立ち止まり迷っても　微笑んで受けとめればいい\Nまっすぐ胸を張り　歩きだそう}
Dialogue: 5,0:24:38.26,0:24:45.18,Song,,0,0,0,,a cold, strong wind will blow to stop you
Dialogue: 5,0:24:46.12,0:25:02.01,Song,,0,0,0,,Continuing to walk as you please is nice,\Nbut you may feel lonely and want to cry along the way
Dialogue: 5,0:25:02.01,0:25:11.01,Song,,0,0,0,,But believe in yourself, \Nbecause it's what you decided, don't waver
Dialogue: 5,0:25:11.01,0:25:19.29,Song,,0,0,0,,See, the world gets more wonderful \Nevery time it opens up
Dialogue: 5,0:25:19.29,0:25:28.27,Song,,0,0,0,,If it's a dream you yearn for \Nso passionately, just give it a form
Dialogue: 5,0:25:29.00,0:25:35.28,Song,,0,0,0,,Be stronger, be more enduring
Dialogue: 5,0:25:35.28,0:25:43.90,Song,,0,0,0,,If you stop and waver, \Njust try to remember what it means to be honest
Dialogue: 5,0:25:43.90,0:25:53.74,Song,,0,0,0,,A bright new tomorrow is waiting for you
Dialogue: 5,0:48:20.29,0:48:31.18,Song,,0,0,0,,Like it or not.\NI wonder who was the first to say that {好きとか嫌いとか\N最初に言い出したのは\N誰なのかしら\N駆け抜けてゆく\N私のメモリアル\N今日も鏡のまえで\N髪をとかして\Nピンクのリップは Sweet Magic\Nとっておきのコロン\Nさ・さ・や・き\Nド・キ・ド・キ\Nキ・ラ・メ・キ\N大好き\Nあなただけに見つめて欲しい}
Dialogue: 5,0:48:31.18,0:48:40.28,Song,,0,0,0,,My memorial runs through my heart
Dialogue: 5,0:48:42.96,0:48:49.15,Song,,0,0,0,,I comb my hair in front of the mirror today
Dialogue: 5,0:48:49.15,0:48:54.81,Song,,0,0,0,,Pink lipstick is sweet magic, \Nmy very special cologne
Dialogue: 5,0:48:54.81,0:49:01.15,Song,,0,0,0,,Whispering, twinkling, heart pounding, and loving
Dialogue: 5,0:49:01.15,0:49:08.18,Song,,0,0,0,,I want only you to look at me
Dialogue: 5,0:49:09.47,0:49:10.09,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take the Chance {(Take the Chance)\N仕上げは上出来\N(Tell Your Heart)\N準備はOK\Nステキな予感 そよ風に乗せ\N(Try Your Luck)\N制服のリボン\N(Tell Your Love)\N結び直したら\N今日こそ言えそう“Love me please…”\Nわたしのこの思い\Nあなたは気付いているの?\N気付いてないの?\Nおしえてあげる\Nときめきメモリアル}{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:49:10.09,0:49:12.53,Song,,0,0,0,,Great finishing touches
Dialogue: 5,0:49:12.53,0:49:13.37,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell Your Heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:49:13.37,0:49:15.21,Song,,0,0,0,,I've prepared myself
Dialogue: 5,0:49:15.21,0:49:21.40,Song,,0,0,0,,A wonderful feeling, carried by the breeze
Dialogue: 5,0:49:21.40,0:49:22.40,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try Your Luck{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:49:22.40,0:49:24.62,Song,,0,0,0,,My uniform ribbon
Dialogue: 5,0:49:24.62,0:49:25.66,Song,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell Your Love{\i0}
Dialogue: 5,0:49:25.66,0:49:27.30,Song,,0,0,0,,I tie it again
Dialogue: 5,0:49:27.30,0:49:33.97,Song,,0,0,0,,Today's the day I can say, "Love me please"
